title: Kings Beat San Antonio in Aldridge's Spurs Debut
text:
Published By: NYTimes Pro-Basketball - Today 
Rudy Gay had 26 points and seven rebounds as the Sacramento Kings beat the San Antonio Spurs 95-92 in a preseason game Thursday night....
